    <div class="field field-name-comment-body field-type-text-long field-label-hidden"><p>Hi Joseph,<br />
Yes - part of teaching a growth mindset, rather than just having one - is helping students to develop resilience.</p>
</div>
  
  <span class="sign-in-link"><a href="/user/login?destination=node/460526#comments">Sign in to vote!</a></span><span class="count-link"></span></article> <!-- /#comment-4 -->
